sights.name: Burg Hasegg / Hall Mint
sights.quote: Medieval castle whose old silver mint (famous as the origin of the word "dollar") is now a museum.
sights.address: Burg Hasegg 6, 6060 Hall in Tirol, Austria

sights.name: Alpine Zoo Innsbruck
sights.quote: Mountainside conservation-minded zoo, for rare Alpine birds & animals from wolves to golden eagles.

sights.name: Innsbrucker Hofgarten
sights.quote: Landscaped royal palace gardens dating from 1410, with a pavilion, butterfly house & restaurant.

sights.name: Dom zu St. Jakob
sights.quote: Grand 18th-century baroque cathedral with an ornate interior & iconic painting of the Virgin Mary.
